descriptionHtml:
Stay connected with your vehicle through your phone and get to know your vehicle and riding patterns more than ever. Locating vehicle, planning trips, requesting services, tracking vehicle’s charging and so much you can do.

Access your riding data on your phone too!





Why is this app a must-have?





1) Available range, service logs, charging cycles and battery behaviour are all at your fingertips so you plan your commute accordingly.

2) In the age of digital, park carefree with real time location updates.

3) Locate the nearest authorised service centers, dealer points and charging points for your trips.

4) Requesting roadside assistance and booking services are easier than ever, tap away your worries.

5) OTA software updates, reporting issues with the app are a breeze.

6) A vault for all your documents that might come in handy.

Stay connected with your vehicle through your phone and get to know your vehicle and riding patterns more than ever. Locating vehicle, planning trips, requesting services, tracking vehicle’s charging and so much you can do.

Access your riding data on your phone too!





Why is this app a must-have?





1) Available range, service logs, charging cycles and battery behaviour are all at your fingertips so you plan your commute accordingly.

2) In the age of digital, park carefree with real time location updates.

3) Locate the nearest authorised service centers, dealer points and charging points for your trips.

4) Requesting roadside assistance and booking services are easier than ever, tap away your worries.

5) OTA software updates, reporting issues with the app are a breeze.

6) A vault for all your documents that might come in handy.

Our product portfolio includes- E scooters & E cycles. Batt:RE is our contribution towards reducing carbon footprint, tackling noise pollution, better traffic conditions and creating a Greener Planet. At BattRE, our focus is to introduce high-quality electric scooters at affordable prices backed by world-class service support.



Everything starts with people here at Batt:RE – where we look, listen and design around their needs.



And it’s why this baby is full of practical, versatile features that’ll be your ‘support’ system whenever you need them to be.



Designed to look good and work flawlessly, it makes life less worrying and complicated and ensures that you fully utilise its capacity.



We would like to express our sincere appreciation towards your patience and companionship. For more information, please visit www.battre.in

title: BattRE

creator: REVOS AUTO TECH PTE. LTD.
descriptionHtml:
BattRE simplifies how you manage calls and messages while riding. With a streamlined interface to safely answer calls or send and hear messages, BattRE voice-enabled commands and large buttons let you to focus on riding your 2/3 wheeler

Use voice-control, a broad swipe, or the switches present on the handlebar of the vehicle to navigate through the app seamlessly.

BattRE app asks for the following device permissions as needed:
• Camera: To scan vehicle’s QR code
• Contacts: To select from phone contacts to send crash alerts
• Location: To pair the vehicle and utilize the map
• Phone: To make a call to contact
• Call Logs : To show incoming/outgoing call on cluster panel
• Files: To change vehicle’s image
descriptionShort: Surveying the status of your BattRE E-scooter at your fingertips.
